				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/B%E1%BB%87nh-trung-ho%E1%BA%A1-T%C3%A2y-ph%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-bi%E1%BA%BFn-t%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-t%E1%BB%A5ng/poem-ShIAfpMz4LBWa8yMWlhD_w">Bệnh trung hoạ Tây phương biến tương tụng - 病中畫西方變相頌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C4%83n-Ng%E1%BA%A1n-B%C3%A1c/Cung-tr%C3%BAc-tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng/poem-7pLJZPTOqXk91eBFyk5SZQ">Cung trúc trượng - 邛竹杖</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C4%83n-Ng%E1%BA%A1n-B%C3%A1c/author-3f-_gwzHi_bamfFWfl14VQ">Văn Ngạn Bác</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Huy-%C3%8Dch/%C4%90%C3%A1o-gia-qu%C3%A1n-h%E1%BB%89-ph%C3%BA/poem-FdJhbTfX01Vg5O7IswCt9Q">Đáo gia quán hỉ phú - 到家貫喜賦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Huy-%C3%8Dch/author-geNjG6kbAxWPLaqdF181sQ">Phan Huy Ích</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/%C4%90%E1%BB%99c-Gia-Vi%C3%AAn-phu-nh%C3%A2n-th%C3%A1o-ph%E1%BB%8Fng-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-Nham-ni-c%C3%B4-giai-t%C3%A1c-h%E1%BB%AFu-c%E1%BA%A3m-b%E1%BB%99-v%E1%BA%ADn-tr%C3%ACnh-ch%C3%ADnh/poem-8lYK4yot9dQRNH-7Rv_tjw">Độc Gia Viên phu nhân tháo phỏng Tuyết Nham ni cô giai tác hữu cảm bộ vận trình chính - 讀葭園夫人造訪雪岩尼姑佳作有感步韻呈政</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/author-eQ6wft6d1E9_uEITUaRRlg">Nguyễn Phúc Ưng Bình</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Huy%C3%AAn/H%E1%BA%A1-%E1%BA%A5p-nh%C3%A2n-Th%E1%BA%A1ch-Th%E1%BA%A5t-c%E1%BB%B1u-huy%E1%BB%87n-do%C3%A3n-l%E1%BB%A5c-th%E1%BA%ADp-h%E1%BB%B1u-nh%E1%BA%A5t-chi-th%E1%BB%8D/poem-nZT9RmA2kMC1SNFar5YwbQ">Hạ ấp nhân Thạch Thất cựu huyện doãn lục thập hựu nhất chi thọ - 賀邑人石室舊縣尹六十又一之壽</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Huy%C3%AAn/author-h3EvqeQvlQUxq2sceUWWYQ">Đoàn Huyên</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/L%E1%BB%A5c-ti%C3%AAu-2/poem-xsy66Nt3K6ybWaVvKkRV4Q">Lục tiêu 2 - 蓼蕭 2</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/author-Ghtg3UHpaIYXCkHiqunT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Thi%E1%BB%87u-Ung/Nh%C3%A2n-sinh-nh%E1%BA%A5t-th%E1%BA%BF-ng%C3%A2m/poem-FIrQIKjyHyrp8ZEbLVmwfQ">Nhân sinh nhất thế ngâm - 人生一世吟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Thi%E1%BB%87u-Ung/author-o_-PSNPz1uLA6fktF-flfQ">Thiệu Ung</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Huy-%C3%8Dch/S%C6%A1-v%C4%83n-T%C3%B4n-t%E1%BB%95ng-%C4%91%E1%BB%91c-tho%C3%A1i-s%C6%B0-X%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Giang-ng%E1%BA%ABu-ph%C3%BA/poem-o2qDJRw5VrQii8qPMhypOA">Sơ văn Tôn tổng đốc thoái sư Xương Giang ngẫu phú - 初聞孫總督退師昌江偶賦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Huy-%C3%8Dch/author-geNjG6kbAxWPLaqdF181sQ">Phan Huy Ích</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C3%81i-T%C3%A2n-Gi%C3%A1c-La-Ho%E1%BA%B1ng-L%E1%BB%8Bch/T%C3%A2n-ch%C3%ADnh-Tr%C3%B9ng-Hoa-cung-th%E1%BB%8B-ho%C3%A0ng-th%C3%A1i-h%E1%BA%ADu/poem-vZardVE52EY46DKXVpAhlg">Tân chính Trùng Hoa cung thị hoàng thái hậu - 新正重華宮侍皇太后</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C3%81i-T%C3%A2n-Gi%C3%A1c-La-Ho%E1%BA%B1ng-L%E1%BB%8Bch/author-LWiJ3ebJ3gpU86_3bbLouw">Ái Tân Giác La Hoằng Lịch</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Huy-%C3%8Dch/Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-ng%E1%BA%ABu-ch%C3%AD/poem-_PYsjoX1jEKbPwDIlBG6CQ">Thượng Tương ngẫu chí - 上湘偶誌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Huy-%C3%8Dch/author-geNjG6kbAxWPLaqdF181sQ">Phan Huy Ích</a>)<br></div>	</div>
